name: Felix Jaehn
description: '''Fee Jähn''' (born 28 August 1994 as '''Felix Kurt Jähn''', {{IPA|de|ˈfeːlɪks kʊʁt jɛːn|pron}}), known professionally as '''Felix Jaehn''', is a German DJ and record producer. Jaehn achieved international success with their [[remix]] of [[Omi (singer)|OMI]]'s song "[[Cheerleader (Omi song)|Cheerleader]]", which topped the charts in multiple countries and reached number-one on the [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]] in 2015.
